  - Description: Attending Computer Science Conference 2025. Registration paid. Confirmation sent to cs_conference.registration@gmail.com.

Current account balance
- After the $200 payment, your account balance is $1610.00.

If you want
- I can forward the confirmation email I sent to any additional addresses, or add other participants to the calendar event.
- I can look up travel/hotel options near the venue and book them if you’d like.
